  "page": "Eysen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Eysen</b> is a place in the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>; its location has not been revealed. The far-traveled singer <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_of_Eysen\" title=\"Alaric of Eysen\">Alaric</a> comes from Eysen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eysen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Eysen is a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to a friend, writer <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phyllis_Eisenstein\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Phyllis Eisenstein\">Phyllis Eisenstein</a>. <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> is dedicated to Phyllis, \"who made [George] put the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> in.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eysen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Appendix\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/george-r-r-martin-the-rolling-stone-interview-20140423\">George R.R. Martin: The Rolling Stone Interview</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Unknown\" title=\"Template:Region Unknown\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_Unknown&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region Unknown (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_Unknown&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this te